==English==

===Adjective===
'''pointless''' (''no [[comparative]] or [[superlative]]'')
# Having no prominent or important feature, as of an argument, discourse, etc.
#:''a pointless remark''
# Wanting keenness; having no well-defined termination.
#:''a pointless sword''

====Synonyms====
*[[blunt]], [[obtuse]], [[dull]], [[stupid]]

===Adverb===
'''pointlessly'''
# Without point.

===Noun===
'''pointlessness'''
# Total lack of meaning or ideas.